/li></ol><h1 id="修改yml文件"><a href="#修改yml文件" class="headerlink" title="修改yml文件"></a>修改yml文件</h1><ol><li>打开<code>/source/_data/about.yml</code>，将如下代码进行替换,大约在30行到40行：</li></ol><figure class="highlight diff"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="deletion">- careers:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-   tips: 生涯</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-   title: 无限进步</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-   list:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-     - desc: EDU,软件工程专业</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-       color: &quot;#357ef5&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-     - desc: EDU,软件工程专业</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-       color: &quot;#357ef5&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-     - desc: EDU,软件工程专业</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-       color: &quot;#357ef5&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-   img: https://bu.dusays.com/2023/04/21/644287166329b.png</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="addition">+ loveNotes:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="addition">+   tips: 恋爱记</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="addition">+   time: 2099/09/09 00:00:00</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="addition">+   title: 纪念点点滴滴</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="addition">+   name: D&amp;Z</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="addition">+   img: xxx.png // 背景图</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li>如下是可以复制的代码：</li></ol><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">loveNotes:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">tips:</span> <span class="string">恋爱记</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">time:</span> <span class="number">2099</span><span class="string">/09/09</span> <span class="number">00</span><span class="string">:00:00</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">纪念点点滴滴</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">D&amp;Z</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">img:</span> <span class="string">xxx.png</span> <span class="string">//</span> <span class="string">背景图</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>参考文章：<a href="https://byer.top/posts/4c616cdb.html">https://byer.top/posts/4c616cdb.html</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
